    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Copper alloy containing silicon, either in small or larger amounts depending on the class, used for electrical wires due to its strength and resistance to corrosion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
